<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <title>Home - Tutors</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/fonts/font-awesome.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/fonts/ionicons.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/3.5.2/animate.min.css">


    <style media="screen">
      #chat-google{
        position: fixed;
        bottom: 40px;
        right: 50px;
        cursor: pointer;
      }
      #chat-github{
        position: fixed;
        bottom: 95px;
        right: 50px;
        cursor: pointer;
      }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-light navbar-expand-lg fixed-top" id="mainNav" style="font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;">
        <div class="container">
          <a class="navbar-brand" href="/" style="font-size: 30px;">Tutors</a>
          <button class="navbar-toggler" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarResponsive" aria-controls="navbarResponsive" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation"><i class="fa fa-bars"></i></button>
            <div
                class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarResponsive">
                <ul class="nav navbar-nav text-center ml-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item" role="presentation" style="padding-top: 20px;"><a class="nav-link" href="/">Home</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item" role="presentation" style="padding-top: 20px;"><a class="nav-link" href="/about">About us</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item" role="presentation" style="padding-top: 20px;"><a class="nav-link" href="/contact-us">Contact us</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item" role="presentation" style="padding-top: 20px;"><a class="nav-link" href="/assignments">Assignments</a></li>
                    <% if(!user){ %>
                      <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/signin"><button class="btn btn-primary" type="button">Login</button></a>
                      </li>
                      <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/signup"><button class="btn btn-primary" type="button">Signup</button></a>
                      </li>
                    <% } %>
                    <% if(user){ %>
                      <% if(user.status == 'Faculty'){ %>
                        <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
                          <a class="nav-link" href="/faculty-profile"><button class="btn btn-danger" type="button"><%= user.name %></button></a>
                        </li>
                      <% } else{ %>
                        <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
                          <a class="nav-link" href="/profile"><button class="btn btn-primary" type="button"><%= user.name %></button></a>
                        </li>
                      <% } %>
                      <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/logout"><button class="btn btn-primary" type="button">Logout</button></a>
                      </li>
                    <% } %>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <header class="masthead" style="background-image:url('assets/img/home-bg.jpg');">
        <div class="overlay"></div>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-10 col-lg-8 mx-auto">
                    <div class="site-heading">
                        <h1>Awesome Tutors</h1>
                        <span class="subheading" style="font-family: Calibri; margin-top: 35px;">We are the legends in field of providing education with the aim of educating the world with best education and resources.</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="container" style="margin: 70px auto;">
      <div class="section">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-4" style="margin-top: -40px;">
            <img src="boy-laptop.jpg" alt="boy studying on laptop" height="100%" width="100%">
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-8">
            <h1>Our Aim</h1>
            <h4 style="font-family: Calibri; margin-top: 20px;">"Make India largest educated country"</h4>
            <p class="lead" style="font-family: Calibri; margin-top: 0;">
              We started in 1957 with the aim of educating India with the best of the resources, providing
              correct and accurate way to touch any topic, increasing solving ability of students, and with a lot
              more motives. We are aiming towards making the world's largest educated country with the maximum
              number of literate people in the world. Our aim is making India Proud.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr>

    <div class="container">
      <div class="section" style="margin-top: 90px;">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-8">
            <h1>Why join us?</h1>
            <h4 style="font-family: Calibri; margin-top: 20px;">We have the answer for your question.</h4>
            <p class="lead" style="font-family: Calibri;">
              We at Logic Tutors work hard and give our 100% to teach every child with the best of our knowledge,
              and resources. We have the best faculties of Delhi who have the experience of more than
              10 years in their respective fields. They are contributing for the Logic Tutors since last
              8-10 years and made us proud by taking us to the top of Delhi's best coaching. Our alumni
              work in the world's most prime companies. So would you love to join us and become part
              of world's largest education hub.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr>

    <% if(!user) { %>
      <div class="container" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 40px;">
          <h2 style="font-family: Calibri; ">We have a special login method for faculties.</h2>
          <p style="font-family: Basic, sans-serif;">Now you can track the student work..</p>
          <a class="nav-link" href="/faculty-signin"><button class="btn btn-danger" type="button">Login</button></a>
      </div>
    <% } %>

    <hr>
    <div class="container" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 80px; font-family: Calibri;">
      <h1>Where do we exist?</h1>
      <p class="lead">You can also find us in Netaji Nagar. Use maps to get directions.</p>
      <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d7007.680698186698!2d77.18144202525147!3d28.574556429762577!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x390d1d783838fb5d%3A0xb19642d3e39b27ac!2sNetaji+Nagar%2C+New+Delhi%2C+Delhi+110023!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1554741177473!5m2!1sen!2sin" width="100%" height="450" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
    </div>
    <footer>
      <hr>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-10 col-lg-8 mx-auto">
                    <ul class="list-inline text-center">
                        <li class="list-inline-item"><span class="fa-stack fa-lg"><i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x"></i><i class="fa fa-twitter fa-stack-1x fa-inverse" data-bs-hover-animate="tada"></i></span></li>
                        <li class="list-inline-item"><span class="fa-stack fa-lg"><i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x"></i><i class="fa fa-facebook fa-stack-1x fa-inverse" data-bs-hover-animate="tada"></i></span></li>
                        <li class="list-inline-item"><span class="fa-stack fa-lg"><i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x"></i><i class="fa fa-instagram fa-stack-1x fa-inverse" data-bs-hover-animate="tada"></i></span></li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="lead text-muted copyright" style="font-size: 19px;">Copyright&nbsp;Â©&nbsp;Tutors 2019, Created by <a href="https://saurabh-portfolio.herokuapp.com" style="text-decoration: none;">Saurabh Panchal</a></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <span class="fa-stack fa-lg" id="chat-google"><i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x" style="color: #C0392B;"></i><i class="fa fa-google fa-stack-1x fa-inverse" data-bs-hover-animate="tada"></i></span>
    <span class="fa-stack fa-lg" id="chat-github"><i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x"></i><i class="fa fa-github fa-stack-1x fa-inverse" data-bs-hover-animate="tada"></i></span>

    <script src="assets/js/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="assets/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="assets/js/bs-animation.js"></script>
    <script src="assets/js/clean-blog.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
